If like us you can‚Äôt you can try lowering the status frames of the motor controller‚Äôs and such we have found that the spark Max‚Äôs were the biggest user of the can and you can set them so that they won‚Äôt send status frames periodically only when called and that lowered the can usage by like 10 percent for 4 motors
